title: Oceanic Gaming Test Tourney

embed.description: Battlefy is the simplest way to start, manage, and find esports tournaments | Create. Compete. Conquer.

body:
Oceanic Gaming are running their very first League of Legends tournament.
Data collected from the tournaments will be used to create a better tournament experience for future tournaments.

Prizes are supplied by Riot Games. Comes along test if you have what it takes.
